OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day then remaining dry
OL,7,Fovernight with long clear spells.
OL,8,FBecoming rather chilly overnight with
OL,9,Fsome patchy mist developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FEarly mist soon clearing then
OL,12,Fa dry day with long spells of
OL,13,Fsunshine. Becoming quite warm inland
OL,14,Fbut cooler with some mist along the
OL,15,Feast coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA dry
OL,18,Ffew days with good spells of sunshine.
OL,19,FWarm in the west with the best of the
OL,20,Fsunshine, cloudier and cooler at times
OL,21,Fin the east.
